  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Social media executive",
  "description": "<p>ob Title:</p><p>Social Media Executive (Fresh Graduates Welcome)</p><p></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for a creative and motivated Social Media Executive to join our team. This role is suitable for fresh graduates or school leavers who are passionate about social media, content creation, and digital marketing. You will be involved in managing our social media platforms and supporting online marketing activities to grow brand awareness and engagement.</p><p><br /></p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Create, plan, and schedule content for social media platforms such as Instagram, Facebook, TikTok, and others</li><li>Assist in photo and video shooting, editing short-form videos (Reels / TikTok)</li><li>Write captions and simple marketing content in English and Chinese</li><li>Monitor social media messages, comments, and customer engagement</li><li>Support promotions, campaigns, and product launches</li><li>Stay updated with social media trends and competitor activities</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Fresh graduates / fresh from school are welcome</li><li>Must be able to read, write, and communicate in Chinese</li><li>Good command of English</li><li>Strong interest in social media, digital marketing, or lifestyle brands</li><li>Basic skills in Canva, CapCut, or similar editing tools</li><li>Willing to learn, proactive, and responsible</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>What We Offer:</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>On-the-job training provided</li><li>Friendly and supportive working environment</li><li>Opportunity to grow in social media and digital marketing</li><li>Career progression opportunities</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>📩 To apply:</p><p>Please send your resume and portfolio (if any) to</p><p>Email: pohandy@gmail.com</p>",
